      "difficulty": "intermediate",
      "problem": "ಸಂಕ್ಷೇಪಿಸಿ: (i) 2^(2/3) ⋅ 2^(1/3) (ii) (3^(1/5))^4 (iii) 7^(1/5) / 7^(1/3)",
